5G的攝像頭組合，為遠攝攝像頭選擇了不同的傳感器和鏡頭規格，為散景拍攝拋棄了飛行時間傳感器。在大多情況下，三星GALAXY NOTE20 ULTRA 5G圖像質量優秀，三星的高端機型個個曝光、細節俱佳，顏色鮮活，三星GALAXY NOTE20 ULTRA 5G也非例外。所以它在我們數據庫中排名靠前當之無愧。但主要問題是近距和中距的變焦能力，影響了優異表現，進而不能在DXOMARK CAMERA數據庫中的排名更進一步。」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">真的這麼差嗎？可能大家都會對 DxO 的評分產生疑問，不過無論如何規矩是人家定立的，接不接受就消費者們請自行定論了。</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T09:18:28.000Z","msg":"但真係堅唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T09:19:15.000Z","msg":"點唔掂a"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T09:20:11.000Z","msg":"影近野周圍發虛幾嚴重"},{"pid":"24f5c1e26ece30b073674d0c96e8c4e631f772dc","tid":2234681,"uid":302348,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"381ab316040ee4c1d0d31b2cba99b755f27ebb99","tid":2234681,"uid":194606,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"仲Dxo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收皮啦<br />\n冇人想知分數呀<br />\n買分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係人都知邊部真正最靚相機㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T09:20:16.000Z","msg":"Huawei？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76209b2b9286f7996e32b384c847e6e7da573d0c","tid":2234681,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"24f5c1e26ece30b073674d0c96e8c4e631f772dc","tid":2234681,"uid":302348,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"381ab316040ee4c1d0d31b2cba99b755f27ebb99","tid":2234681,"uid":194606,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"仲Dxo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收皮啦<br />\n冇人想知分數呀<br />\n買分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係人都知邊部真正最靚相機㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"